isChangeMenu = false
inSession = false
local sessionId = 0
local prop = nil
local smoking = false 
local heaters = {}  
local closestId = 1
Citizen.CreateThread(function()
    while PlayerData == nil do Citizen.Wait(1000) end
    ESX.TriggerServerCallback('ak47_hookahlounge:gettabledata', function(data)
        Config.Tables = data
    end)

    local playerPed = PlayerPedId()
    local coords = GetEntityCoords()
    local dist = 0
    local data = nil
    while true do
        Citizen.Wait(0)

        coords = GetEntityCoords(playerPed)

        if dist < data.radius then
            if data.tobaco then
                if not inSession and data.usable == 1 then
                    DrawText3D(vector3(data.pos.x, data.pos.y, data.pos.z + 0.6), _U('t_level', math.ceil(data.t_level)) .. '%'.._U('price', data.price) .. '\n'.._U('use'), Config.Marker.fontSize, Config.Marker.font)

                        ESX.TriggerServerCallback('ak47_hookahlounge:hasenoughmoney', function(cb)
                            if cb then
                                inSession = true
                                sessionId = closestId
                                TriggerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:notify', _U('session_start', data.price))

                                    local x,y,z = table.unpack(GetEntityCoords(playerPed))
                                    local prop_name = "v_corp_lngestoolfd"
                                    prop = CreateObject(GetHashKey(prop_name), x, y, z + 0.2,  true,  true, true)
                                    AttachEntityToEntity(prop, playerPed, GetPedBoneIndex(playerPed, 18905), -0.26, -0.54, 0.28, -90.00000001, -868.00000001, -361.00000001, true, true, false, true, 1, true)
                                    TriggerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:smokeenter')

                                        Citizen.Wait(0)
                                        ESX.ShowHelpNotification(_U('smoke'))
                                        playerPed = PlayerPedId()
                                        coords = GetEntityCoords(playerPed)
                                        local distance = #(coords - Config.Tables[sessionId].pos)
                                        if distance > Config.Tables[sessionId].radius then

                                            ESX.Game.DeleteObject(prop)
                                            ClearPedTasks(playerPed)
                                            TriggerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:notify', _U('moved_far'))
                                        end
                                        if IsControlJustReleased(1, 38) and not smoking then
                                            if Config.Tables[sessionId].usable == 1 then
                                                smoking = true  
                                                TriggerServerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:onuse', sessionId)
                                                TriggerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:smoke')
                                            else
                                                inSession = false
                                                ESX.Game.DeleteObject(prop)
                                                ClearPedTasks(playerPed)
                                                TriggerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:notify', _U('not_usable'))
                                            end
                                        end
                                    end
                                end)
                            end
                        end, data.price)
                        Citizen.Wait(1000)
                    end
                elseif inSession and data.usable == 1 then

                    if IsControlJustReleased(1, 74) then
                        inSession = false
                        ESX.Game.DeleteObject(prop)
                        ClearPedTasks(playerPed)
                    end

            else
                Citizen.Wait(1000)
            end
        else
            Citizen.Wait(1000)
        end
    end
end)

Citizen.CreateThread(function()
    local playerPed = PlayerPedId()
    local coords = GetEntityCoords()
    local dist = 0
    while true do
        Citizen.Wait(1000)
        local tempDis = 100
        local tempClosest = 1
        playerPed = PlayerPedId()
        coords = GetEntityCoords(playerPed)
        for i = 1, #Config.Tables, 1 do
            dist = #(coords - Config.Tables[i].pos)
            if dist < tempDis then
                tempDis = dist
                tempClosest = i
            end
        end
        closestId = tempClosest
    end
end)

RegisterNetEvent("ak47_hookahlounge:smokeenter")
AddEventHandler("ak47_hookahlounge:smokeenter", function()
    local ped = GetPlayerPed(-1)
    local ad = "mp_player_inteat@burger"
    local anim = "mp_player_int_eat_burger_enter"
    if (DoesEntityExist(ped) and not IsEntityDead(ped)) then
        while (not HasAnimDictLoaded(ad)) do
            RequestAnimDict(ad)
            Wait(1)
        end
        TaskPlayAnim(ped, ad, anim, 1.00000001, 1.00000001, -1, (2 + 16 + 32), 0.00000001, 0, 0, 0)
    end
    smoking = false
end)

RegisterNetEvent("ak47_hookahlounge:smoke")
AddEventHandler("ak47_hookahlounge:smoke", function()
    local ped = GetPlayerPed(-1)
    local ad = "mp_player_intdrink"
    local anim = "intro_bottle"
    if (DoesEntityExist(ped) and not IsEntityDead(ped)) then
        while (not HasAnimDictLoaded(ad)) do
            RequestAnimDict(ad)
            Wait(1)
        end
        TaskPlayAnim(ped, ad, anim, 8.00000001, 1.00000001, -1, (2 + 16 + 32), 0.00000001, 0, 0, 0)
    end
    Citizen.Wait(1000)
    TriggerServerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:PlayWithinDistance', Config.Tables[sessionId].pos, 10, 'inhal')
    Citizen.Wait(2000)
    TriggerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:smokeenter')
    TriggerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:playfacial')
end)

RegisterNetEvent("ak47_hookahlounge:playfacial")
AddEventHandler("ak47_hookahlounge:playfacial", function()
    local animDict = 'facials@gen_male@base'
    local animName = 'smoking_hold_1'
    local ped = GetPlayerPed(-1)
    RequestAnimDict(animDict)
    while not HasAnimDictLoaded(animDict) do
        Citizen.Wait(0)
    end
    PlayFacialAnim(ped, animName, animDict)
    TriggerServerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:PlayWithinDistance', GetEntityCoords(PlayerPedId()), 10, 'exhal')
    TriggerServerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:mouthSmoke', 2.5, PedToNet(ped))
    Citizen.Wait(200)
    TriggerServerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:mouthSmoke', 1.00000001, PedToNet(ped))
    Citizen.Wait(200)
    TriggerServerEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:mouthSmoke', 0.7, PedToNet(ped))
end)

RegisterNetEvent('ak47_hookahlounge:mouthSmoke')
AddEventHandler("ak47_hookahlounge:mouthSmoke", function(scale, ped)
    local dict = 'scr_family5'
    local particleName = 'scr_fam_bong_smoke'
    local scale =  scale
    local playerPed = NetToPed(ped)
    local myPed = PlayerPedId()
    if DoesEntityExist(playerPed) and #(GetEntityCoords(myPed) - GetEntityCoords(playerPed)) < 25.0 then
        RequestNamedPtfxAsset(dict)
        while not HasNamedPtfxAssetLoaded(dict) do
            Citizen.Wait(0)
        end
        UseParticleFxAssetNextCall(dict)
        local particleHandle = StartNetworkedParticleFxLoopedOnEntityBone(particleName, playerPed, tofloat(-0.02), tofloat(0.1), tofloat(0.0), tofloat(0.0), tofloat(0.0), tofloat(0.0), GetPedBoneIndex(playerPed,31086), scale, false, false, false)
        SetParticleFxLoopedColour(particleHandle, 0, 255, 0 ,0)
        Citizen.Wait(1000)
        StopParticleFxLooped(particleHandle, false)
    end
end)

RegisterNetEvent("ak47_hookahlounge:tableupdate")
AddEventHandler("ak47_hookahlounge:tableupdate", function(data)
    Config.Tables = data
end)

function createHeaters()
    for i = 1, #Config.Heaters, 1 do
        local prop = CreateObject(GetHashKey('prop_cooker_03'), Config.Heaters[i].pos.x, Config.Heaters[i].pos.y, Config.Heaters[i].pos.z,  false,  false, false)
        SetEntityCoords(prop, Config.Heaters[i].pos.x, Config.Heaters[i].pos.y, Config.Heaters[i].pos.z)
        SetEntityHeading(prop, Config.Heaters[i].heading)
        FreezeEntityPosition(prop,true)
        table.insert(heaters, prop)
    end
end

AddEventHandler('onResourceStop', function(resource)
    if resource == GetCurrentResourceName() then
        for i = 1, #heaters, 1 do
            ESX.Game.DeleteObject(heaters[i])
        end
    end
end)
